{"tid":2343638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反修例風波後投考輔警人數上升　增幅以中年人為主","createTime":"2020-12-28T05:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T11:54:52.000Z","uid":184465,"like":2,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"28cdbaad670e3d22984f517a36e63396c165b428","tid":2343638,"uid":184465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418117&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=79e2c2ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418117&h=0b4eb7d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418117</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】反修例風波後，投考警隊的人數下跌，相反投考輔警的人數上升，30歲或以上的人所佔的比例大幅增加；但投考輔警的大學生明顯減少。<strong><span class=\"red\">輔警方面認為，年青人對警隊有誤解，會加強宣傳。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前輔警學員舉行畢業禮，今年41歲的Ken是其中一位畢業輔警。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">畢業輔警Ken：「看到香港一個這麼好的地方受到這麼嚴重的破壞，我感到十分痛心。我在香港土生土長，見到自己有能力出一分力是義不容辭。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n像Ken一樣，人到中年才投考輔警，在反修例運動後大幅增加。在2019至20年度31至40歲及41至50歲的投考者，比例大增至兩成六及一成半；更罕有地有50歲以上的人投考。<br />\n<br />\n少於30歲的投考者之前佔最多，達到八成七，去年中反修例風波發生後減至五成八。而2019/20年度投考輔警的總人數，較之前一年增加近一倍。<br />\n<br />\n輔警總警司梁世光指，往年透過大學生計劃每年可招募100至120人；反修例示威後減至只有30至40人，近期開始回升。<br />\n<br />\n輔警總警司梁世光：「由於社會事件，特別大學內的人對警隊工作有誤解，但我們相信這個狀況是暫時性。近期招募，我們開始看到有大學生投考這份工作。」<br />\n<br />\n梁世光指，增加投考輔警的中年人當中不少是<strong><span class=\"red\">為人父母</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">梁世光：「他們覺得有這個義務，香港人一起守護這個家，他覺得有這個責任他們亦希望透過輔警這份職業給家中的子女看，這是正當的行為。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n梁世光說，年紀較大的投考人士個別體能不太好，但卻更為有心，所以輔警特別安排督察義務為有需要的投考人士額外進行體能訓練。"},{"pid":"d1de37014d5dc877ba4f8904b751e28a7038150d","tid":2343638,"uid":274772,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"不是垃圾<br />\n<br />\n不做警賊"},{"pid":"f1792a664f6d14ea371cb2433f554acb5146daad","tid":2343638,"uid":206310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:55:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾新聞 拉"},{"pid":"12fa26d89cacce4d344bf6f18968a42b14642bc7","tid":2343638,"uid":50386,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"咪即係班藍絲又想做狗<br />\n但又唔想全職做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d8f60a8a3855a1a3db03a2de98cab6f4d00d43","tid":2343638,"uid":274772,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"一定要做警賊才能給子女做正當行為?<br />\n<br />\n全無邏輯<br />\n<br />\n其他工作好邪惡?<br />\n<br />\n咁全港的人都要做至啱<br />\n<br />\nON9無極限<br />\n<br />\n貪錢就貪錢啦   扮咩撚嘢  垃圾"},{"pid":"22f8b6c408a247e8ae0d6ee3ae8dfed25a090d8c","tid":2343638,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"老人院化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351c35852457bd82b9eec0f1abb88fdb3fe06dcf","tid":2343638,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"另類看更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c09bedbf591594c338a52dacb69103c05c66235","tid":2343638,"uid":171668,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"351c35852457bd82b9eec0f1abb88fdb3fe06dcf","tid":2343638,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"另類看更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"以